###

## Get all location zones with filters
GET {{baseURL}}/zones?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Get zones by city
GET {{baseURL}}/zones?city=Mumbai&page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Get zones by service type
GET {{baseURL}}/zones?serviceType=both_vendor_home_chef&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Get zones by coordinates (within radius)
GET {{baseURL}}/zones?lat=19.0760&lng=72.8777&radius=10&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Search zones by text
GET {{baseURL}}/zones?search=Downtown&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Get specific location zone by ID
GET {{baseURL}}/zones/{{zoneId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Check service availability by pincode
GET {{baseURL}}/zones/check-service/{{pincode}}?vendorType=food_vendor
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Validate delivery for subscription (NEW API)
POST {{baseURL}}/zones/validate-delivery
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "deliveryAddress": {
        "street": "123 Main Street, Apartment 4B",
        "city": "Mumbai",
        "state": "Maharashtra",
        "country": "India",
        "zipCode": "400001",
        "landmark": "Near Metro Station",
        "coordinates": {
            "type": "Point",
            "coordinates": [72.8777, 19.0760]
        }
    },
    "subscriptionCategory": "food_vendor"
}

###

## Calculate delivery fee for a zone
GET {{baseURL}}/zones/{{zoneId}}/delivery-fee?distance=5&orderValue=300
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Update location zone
PUT {{baseURL}}/admin/zones/{{zoneId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
    "zoneName": "Updated Downtown Zone",
    "serviceRadius": 15,
    "deliveryFee": {
        "baseCharge": 60,
        "perKmCharge": 6
    }
}

###

## Toggle zone status
PATCH {{baseURL}}/admin/zones/{{zoneId}}/toggle-status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

## Delete location zone
DELETE {{baseURL}}/admin/zones/{{zoneId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

